dc_title_s: Suite de la carte de l'Inde en deçà du Gange: IIe. feuille, comprenant la Presqu' Isle de l'Inde: pour servir à l'Histoire générale des voyages.
dc_description_s: Scale approximately 1:9,000,000. Covers India north to Bombay. Also covers Sri Lanka. Relief shown pictorially. From: Histoire générale des voyages ... Paris : Didot, 1746-1789. "No. 2 Tome X in 4° Page 1"--Lower left margin. "Tome 5 in 8° Page 116 No. 2"--Lower right margin. Includes decorative cartouche. 21 x 24 cm
